ata-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fyx1665702980810.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fyx1665702980810.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fyx1665702980810.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fyx1665702980810\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n Character Display Attributes \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__character_display_attributes_188822\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Each character in Fonts 0, 1, 2, 3, 4, and 7 can be formatted using bold, italic, or underline. The collective term for this kind of formatting is a ‘shape’. It applies to text formatting of data, primarily on printers.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__p_d63191e1_d63192e1_d63193e1\">By combining each of these attributes, each character in a font can appear in the following different shapes:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__li_d27527e1_d27528e1_d27529e1\">Normal\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__li_d27530e1_d27531e1_d27532e1\">Underline\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__li_d27533e1_d27534e1_d27535e1\">Italics\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__li_d27536e1_d27537e1_d27538e1\">Bold\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__li_d27539e1_d27540e1_d27541e1\">Bold and italics\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__li_d27542e1_d27543e1_d27544e1\">Italics and underline\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__li_d27545e1_d27546e1_d27547e1\">Bold and underline\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__li_d27548e1_d27549e1_d27550e1\">Bold, italics, and underline\n </li>\n</ul>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__topic_d41667e1_d41668e1_d41669e1_d41670e1_d41671e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d420103e84\">\n                       \n IBM Fonts 0-7 and DEC Fonts 0-1\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__p_d63197e1_d63198e1_d63199e1\">For these character sets, each character is preceded by two bytes to indicate the desired character display attribute. The hexadecimal values for these bytes are shown in the table:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__p_d63200e1_d63201e1_d63202e1\">(bol=bold, ita=italic, und=underline)</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"7\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Storing character display attributes for IBM Fonts 0-7 and DEC Fonts 0-1</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__1\">\n und\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__2\">\n ita\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__3\">\n und/ita\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__4\">\n bol\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__5\">\n und/bol\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__6\">\n ita/bol\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__7\">\n und/ita/bol\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__1\">\n 19.28\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__2\">\n 19.30\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__3\">\n 19.38\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__4\">\n 19.40\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__5\">\n 19.48\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__6\">\n 19.50\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5531e1_d5532e1_d5533e1__entry__7\">\n 19.58\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__topic_d41672e1_d41673e1_d41674e1_d41675e1_d41676e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d420103e176\">\n                       \n DEC Fonts 2-7\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__p_d63206e1_d63207e1_d63208e1\">For these character sets, the leading two bytes of each character are replaced by the two bytes shown in the following table (in hexadecimal):</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__p_d63209e1_d63210e1_d63211e1\">(bol=bold, ita=italic, und=underline)</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"9\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Storing character display attributes for DEC Fonts 2-7</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__1\">\n Fonts\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"2\">\n Replace these bytes\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" colspan=\"7\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3\">\n With these bytes for character attributes\n </th>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__4\"></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__5\">\n und\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__6\">\n ita\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__7\">\n und/ita\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__8\">\n bol\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__9\">\n und/bol\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__10\">\n ita/bol\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__11\">\n und/ita/bol\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__1 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__4\">\n 2-3\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__2\">\n 19.22\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__5\">\n 19.2A\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__6\">\n 19.32\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__7\">\n 19.3A\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__8\">\n 19.42\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__9\">\n 19.4A\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__10\">\n 19.52\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__11\">\n 19.5A\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__1 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__4\">\n 4-5\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__2\">\n 19.24\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__5\">\n 19.2C\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__6\">\n 19.34\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__7\">\n 19.3C\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__8\">\n 19.44\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__9\">\n 19.4C\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__10\">\n 19.54\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__11\">\n 19.5C\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__1 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__4\">\n 6-7\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__2\">\n 19.26\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__5\">\n 19.2E\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__6\">\n 19.36\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__7\">\n 19.3E\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__8\">\n 19.46\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__9\">\n 19.4E\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__10\">\n 19.56\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__3 fyx1665702980810__table_d5534e1_d5535e1_d5536e1__entry__11\">\n 19.5E\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fyx1665702980810__p_d63212e1_d63213e1_d63214e1\">For example, the subscript 0 ( 0 ) in Font 3 for DEC is 19.22.B0. When the bold display attribute is applied, this becomes 19.42.B0.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527751\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527751\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Character Display Attributes Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Character Display Attributes Each character in Fonts 0, 1, 2, 3, 4, and 7 can be formatted using bold, italic, or underline. The collective term for this kind of formatting is a ‘shape’. It applies to text formatting of data, primarily on printers. By combining each of these attributes, each character in a font can appear in the following different shapes: Normal Underline Italics Bold Bold and italics Italics and underline Bold and underline Bold, italics, and underline IBM Fonts 0-7 and DEC Fonts 0-1 For these character sets, each character is preceded by two bytes to indicate the desired character display attribute. The hexadecimal values for these bytes are shown in the table: (bol=bold, ita=italic, und=underline) Table 1. Storing character display attributes for IBM Fonts 0-7 and DEC Fonts 0-1 und ita und/ita bol und/bol ita/bol und/ita/bol 19.28 19.30 19.38 19.40 19.48 19.50 19.58 DEC Fonts 2-7 For these character sets, the leading two bytes of each character are replaced by the two bytes shown in the following table (in hexadecimal): (bol=bold, ita=italic, und=underline) Table 2. Storing character display attributes for DEC Fonts 2-7 Fonts Replace these bytes With these bytes for character attributes und ita und/ita bol und/bol ita/bol und/ita/bol 2-3 19.22 19.2A 19.32 19.3A 19.42 19.4A 19.52 19.5A 4-5 19.24 19.2C 19.34 19.3C 19.44 19.4C 19.54 19.5C 6-7 19.26 19.2E 19.36 19.3E 19.46 19.4E 19.56 19.5E For example, the subscript 0 ( 0 ) in Font 3 for DEC is 19.22.B0. When the bold display attribute is applied, this becomes 19.42.B0. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}